#not function. a whitelist on purpose: keywords that really use the dash
#(Boast, Companion) are in neither catalog, so they stay whole. regenerate by
#rerunning the fetch in the commit that made this file. two identical copies
#exist (common/ and web/) because railway only deploys the web folder.

